            "content": "<p>Start with the towel to gently press-dry hair. Detangle with the silk comb from ends to roots. Finish with the boar-bristle brush to smooth and distribute natural oils. Tie with the silk scrunchie \u2014 no breakage, no dents.<\/p>",
